#Task: Before Backend Developer Interview

##This is a task designed to understand the skillset of the developer joining StimVeda Neurosciences. 

The following skillsets are being evaluated - 
1. Practicality of the architecture 
2. Code Readability (Modularity, Documentation)
3. API Design of components/routes
4. Following best practices in web secuirty like IDOR, Input Validation, etc.
5. Speed of execution


##Task 

Design an architecture for a habit tracking app with a set of modules for self development.
